stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OpenChatbot
    OpenChatbot --> TypeMessage
    TypeMessage --> SendMessage : POST /api/chatbot/send/
    SendMessage --> BuildSystemPrompt : Include alert context
    BuildSystemPrompt --> CallOllama : _call_ollama()
    CallOllama --> OllamaProcessing : LLM generates response
    OllamaProcessing --> OllamaSuccess : Response received
    OllamaProcessing --> OllamaFailed : Ollama unavailable
    OllamaFailed --> FallbackEnhanced : Use enhanced mode
    FallbackEnhanced --> DisplayResponse
    OllamaSuccess --> ParseMarkdown
    ParseMarkdown --> DisplayResponse
    DisplayResponse --> TypeMessage
    DisplayResponse --> [*]